IMAPAccount MSmail
Host imap-mail.outlook.com
User Me@theirplace.tld
Pass IfYouDare

UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore ol-remote
Account MSmail

MaildirStore ol-local
Path ~/.mail/ol/
Inbox ~/.mail/ol/Inbox

Channel MSmail
Master :ol-remote:
Slave :ol-local:

Create Both
SyncState *
